    {"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Cultural Context"}],"depth":2,"type":"heading"},
    {"children":[{"type":"text","value":"坚决 embodies Chinese values of strength, determination, and unwavering commitment. In Chinese\nculture, being 坚决 is seen as a virtue, especially in matters of principle and moral conviction. It\nreflects the cultural appreciation for steadfastness and the ability to hold firm positions despite\nchallenges."}],"type":"paragraph"}
